E2T11AU.original: ~z~Or the desert. Like you was just saying to me. Leave town, bro.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~沙漠也行。像你刚才说的那样，赶紧走，兄弟。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~L, thank God. I've been worried sick. How we doing?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~L，谢天谢地。我快担心死了，情况怎样？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Then you're gonna have to punch me out again, Lou!
~z~Come on, T, give me a break.
~z~But I don't want you to get a big head. I don't want you to go change; become a mega star, go to Vinewood, write a blog.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~但我不希望你发飘，不想看到你变样：变成大明星，去好麦坞，写博客啥的。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I'll come find you if all our troubles go away, but if I don't show, you got to run.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~问题解决我就来找你。要是没来，你就该跑了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~This Ray Bulgarin's smack, motherfuckers? Where is he?
~z~The Heights is my home man. Always will be. Nothing's worth shit if I can't go back there.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~高地就是我家，永远的家。要是回不去，一切都没有意义。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I have no fucking clue. Err Dukes?
~z~Fly. Get us the fuck out of here.
~z~He will pay people to come here and kill you.
~z~Don't make me, man. You know you just gonna slow me down, bro, and kill us both. I want at least one of us to survive.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~别逼我，哥们。你也知道自己是拖油瓶，只会害死我们。我俩至少得活一个。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Any other man would just dust himself off and carry on.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~是个人都能重整旗鼓，继续干哦。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I nearly had him, T. I nearly had him. He's gone back to fucking Russia now!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~差点就成功了，T，就差那么一点。还是给他跑回俄罗斯了！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~This man is faggot and you can't kill him?
~z~Yeah, we always had a clientele policy, and you don't cut it.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~哟，我们是有一套招待的方法，可惜你不够格。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Not so good. We got a good man killed doing this shit. Our boy, Yusuf.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~不太好，为此还害死了我们的好兄弟，Yusuf。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You can't shoot me. You will blow whole plane up.
~z~Nah, went to Algonquin instead; waiting for the world to come to me.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~没。最后去Algonquin了，等待世界上门找我。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You are too late to find Mr. Ray. He is leaving country right now.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~现在去找Ray先生已经晚了，他准备出国了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~No. I would have come back to finish things with you.
~z~Maybe you turned your back on where you was from when you was a kid, but that ain't something I can really do.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你是从小就抛下老家走进都市了，但这事我干不出来。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I thought I was the annoying drama queen in this pairing.
~z~Oh shut up, you hysterical fucking queen. Get a grip, bro.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~闭嘴吧，矫揉造作的死基佬。淡定点，哥们。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~What do you need? Let me help out.
~z~Okay, shit. I'll do that. Where should I hide?
~z~Lack of balls was always your problem.
~z~Is sweet of you to see me off.
~z~What do you need? Let me help out.
~z~Mr. Ray flies away now, pretty boy. You are too late to get him.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Ray先生坐飞机走了，小白脸。你来晚了一步。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Okay. I'm armed, I'm dangerous. Let's fucking do this!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~好。我有枪，我很能打，一起干他妈的！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Where's Bulgarin? We got a score to settle.
~z~You think he will forget about you? You and all your friends are dead.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你以为他会一走了之吗？你和你的朋友都死定了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~This is our last chance, ain't it, Lou? We've got to take down Bulgarin and all his people.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~这次是背水一战了，对吧，Lou？必须要干掉Bulgarin和他的手下。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You people try and kill us. Stop it!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你的人要害死我们了，甩掉他！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Oh, yes, silly me. Silly fucking me...huh?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~哦，是，我不好，呵呵呵呵。全是我的错...哼？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Oh, by the way, think my father may be in to franchising the clubs.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~噢，对了，我爸好像有兴趣投资你们的分店。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Yusuf too? Shit. How many people got to go down because of us?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Yusuf挂了？妈的，有多少人因为我们死了？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I don't get what Mr. Ray saw in you.
~z~Yeah I'm serious. You got to hide out out for a bit, T.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~对，认真的。你先去躲一会儿吧，T。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I can't talk, bro. Shit's really coming apart.
~z~We took on this town and we won. We took on this place and we gave it the fucking finger.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我们拿下了自由城，我们赢了。拿下了这座城市，狠狠地鄙视了所有人。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Look, ok, I'm sorry I thought about killing you. I really am. But if you keep up with the bullshit, I might have to kill you for real.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~听我说，好吗，很抱歉我有想过杀了你，对不起。只是你再这样发疯，我很难不杀了你。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Put him down and keep him down.
~z~We are leaving this country now. Go. Go.
~z~He has much money. He will use it to have you killed.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~他有的是钱，拿钱就能买你的命。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Take care of yourself, okay? Stay away from idiots like me.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~小心点，好吗？离我这种傻逼远点。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Tell people Timur and Mr. Ray have serious package now. We own H trade in Liberty.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~传出去，Timur和Ray先生手头有大量货。自由城的海洛因归我们管了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I got some news about that smack, B.
~z~Hey, I don't know what the hell I was thinking hangin with you, asshole.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~都不知道我当时怎么会去找你的，臭逼。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You guys tried to kill me one too many times.
~z~One of my less salubrious associates told me Bulgarin was in on this H deal at Fun Land on Firefly.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~狐朋狗友跟我说Bulgarin在Firefly的游乐园交易海洛因。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You are a stupid man. You know how much that was worth!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你是傻逼吗，知不知道这多值钱！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Stop it back there or I crash into sea!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~把后面的问题解决掉，不然就坠海了！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~There ain't nothing you can do, Yusuf. If this crazy Russian fuck manages to leave the country, it's over for me and Tone.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你帮不到我了，Yusuf。万一被那个疯毛子跑出美国，我和Tone就完蛋了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I'm serious, T. This my last testament.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我是认真的，T。这就是我的遗言。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Cut his fucking head off and bring it to me.
~z~You're serious about this, aren't you? You're gonna walk in there alone.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你是认真的，对吧？你可是要单打独斗啊。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Go somewhere no one's gonna find you. Maybe back to Dukes? Ain't nobody gonna look for you there.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~去别人找不到你的地方。Dukes怎么样？没人会去那儿找你。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You weren't expecting this, were you, assholes?
~z~You guys tried to kill me one too many times.
~z~Are you glad to be back with your homo master?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~回到基佬主子身边，你高兴了吗？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I was angry before you destroyed our heroin!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~现在又把海洛因毁了，你这是火上浇油！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~So, say we find them, what are we gonna do then?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~那，找到他之后，我们要怎么办？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~But I didn't. And now it's you and me, against the world. Okay?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~但我还是没下手。现在，是你和我对抗全世界，好吧？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Word is they're taking on a big heroin shipment at Fun Land on Firefly Island.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~听说他们在Firefly Island的游乐园接收了一大批海洛因。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Okay, cool. Hit up, like, err, that Monoglobe monument thing in Meadows Park. Hang out for a few hours.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~好，可以。你就去草地公园的巨型地球仪那里吧。在那儿等几个小时。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~He has made asshole of me. Kill him.
~z~Stop whatever is going on back there. I'm trying to fly plane.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~别管是什么，赶紧把后面解决了，飞机要起飞了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I have grenade. You kill me we all die.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我有手雷，你杀了我，我们就同归于尽。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Come on, let's get out of here.
~z~It's Bulgarin or us. Or you can shoot us both, and make his life easy for him.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Bulgarin死了，我们活。不然你现在开两枪，帮他省点事。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I heard you were here, man. Yusuf's here to save the day. Again!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~听说你在这儿，哥们。Yusuf「又」来拯救世界啦！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Now Rascalov is dead, we have sole claim to the junk.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Rascalov已经死了，这批货是我们的了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You think he will forget about you? You and all your friends are dead.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你以为他会放过你吗？你和你的朋友都死定了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I heard Bulgarin was moving some smack out at the Fun Land on Firefly Island.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~听说Bulgarin正在Firefly Island的游乐园转移货物。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~We'll leave town and start all over. New clubs, someplace else. If I can do it, you can too.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~离开自由城，重新开始。新的夜店，换个地方。我能做到，你也能。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Dukes? Alright, I'll wait for you in Middle Park by that silly Monoglobe. You are gonna make it, L. I know it.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Dukes？好吧，我在草地公园的巨蠢地球仪那儿等你。~n~你能做到的，L。我知道的。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Two in the chest and two in the head!
~z~Yo, send some money to my mom sometimes, and tell her I love her.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~哟，多给我妈打点钱，告诉她我爱她。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Shit! What is happening in back of plane?
~z~You want to die, be my guest.
~z~You always have to make a scene, don't you?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你是不是非得搞出点大动静？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Mr. Ray will cut his heart out now!
~z~Luis, bro, do not fear, Yusuf's here. I found you, motherfucker.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Luis，哥们，别害怕，Yusuf来了。找到你了，妈个逼的。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Been through the fact you wanted to kill me?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你想杀我的事儿就这么算了？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~And if your brains ain't working right, then I'll make the decision for us, okay?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~要是你脑子转不过来，那就由我来做决定，好吗？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I always told Mr Ray you were too weak.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我早就和Ray先生说过你太弱了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I seen you fight. You're a pussy.
~z~Yeah. 'Cause I came here looking for you.
~z~Now we own junk trade in Liberty. Anyone need package, they must deal with us.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~城里的货全被我们拿下了。谁想要货，只能跟我们交易。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You should not have fucked with our business.
~z~Tony Prince and Luis Lopez could not be stopped.
~z~You're too much of a pussy to do anything.
~z~No one in this whole crazy town is crazy enough to take you down.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~自由城再疯狂，也没人能干掉你这个疯子。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Yusuf's fucking here! A bad ass A-rab with a mechanical camel.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Yusuf闪亮登场！阿拉伯恶霸骑着机械骆驼来啦！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Okay, Lou. Shit. You'll be fine. Shit.
~z~Been through the fact you are far from alone in that desire?
~z~There aren't many places like that left in the City, I'm afraid.
~z~Luis, what's happening? Are we in the clear?
~z~I come with your family when you are dead.
~z~I will enjoy kill your whole family.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我会享受杀你全家的过程的。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I was hoping to see you, Luis.
~z~I'm sorry, T. I couldn't take it. Bulgarin can keep his shipment. We're finished.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~抱歉了，T。我搞不定。Bulgarin的货还在。我们完蛋了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Not too close though, I don't want to give my father the wrong impression.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~也不要太近，我怕被老爸误会成基佬。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Eh-oh, you trying to leave without saying goodbye?
~z~Mr. Ray flies away now, pretty boy. You are too late to get him.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Ray先生坐飞机走了，小白脸。你来晚了一步。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~This is over. It's over. I just want to go some place far away from here and quietly wait to die.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~已经完了，全完了。我只想离自由城越远越好，找个地方等死。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~He the last one. I'm giving up on it. I'm out. Sorry, T. Goodbye.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~他是最后一个。我不干了，我退出。抱歉，T，再见。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Why am I even saying this? Wish me luck, bro.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~说这么多干嘛呢？祝我好运吧，兄弟。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~What the fuck is going on back there?
~z~This your big business idea. Fuck you.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~这就是你的大生意吗，滚你妈的。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Look, T. Don't go home. Don't go to the clubs.
~z~I only hired you because I thought you were dumb.
~z~You're a pill popping old queen, man. I'm a murdering maniac.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你是个嗑药的黄脸基佬，哥们。我是杀人狂。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Luis, you come to wish me goodbye.
~z~Yo, T., T., gimme a hug, gimme a hug.
~z~Aye Dios Mio. Haven't we been through this already?
~z~I lived it. I lived it hard and now, I'm ready to end it.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我的生活，多年的心血，现在，也该结束了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Come on. Where you think you can hide that no one would expect?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~别啊。有没有那种没人能想到的藏身处？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Yeah, I know. It's a real problem with me. You know? I wish I was more like you - subtle, shy, retiring.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~确实，我这人就这毛病，真的。我挺想像你这样的，内敛、含蓄、羞怯。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I can't talk, bro. Shit's really coming apart.
~z~It ain't like that for me Tone. I still got my family here in LC.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我可不行，Tone。我的家人还在自由城。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Fools must be on the other side.
~z~dreaming of the world. Wondering what it was like that at that place over there, or that little island over there.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~幻想着世界，想象着这个地方长啥样，那个岛长啥样。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~So we're going into exile together. Okay Lou, here's to the open road.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~那我们亡命天涯吧。好了，Lou，庆祝我们光明的未来吧。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Shit. What fucking button do I press?
~z~Shoot, shoot, shoot 'em up. I said, shoot, shoot, shoot 'em up.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~嘭，嘭，嘭嘭嘭。给我嘭，嘭，嘭嘭嘭！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~No, no, franchising is not the way to go. The club is all about the people.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~不不，开分店不是关键，夜店最重要的是人。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I'm massively in debt and I just lost 2 million dollars worth of diamonds.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~欠着一屁股债，还丢了价值两百万的钻石。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Don't go nowhere anyone might conceivably think to look for you.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~别去任何别人觉得你会去的地方。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~They gotta be on the other side the park.
~z~I ran away from there when I was a kid and I swore blind I'd never go back, apart from to catch a plane.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~年轻的时候我就离开那儿了。不赶飞机绝对不会回到那里，我发过毒誓的。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~We gonna take out their income stream and then we gonna take them out. End this bullshit.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~先断掉他的生财之道，然后再赶尽杀绝。做个了断。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Move to Brazil. Move somewhere. Don't ever look back, T.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你去巴西，去哪都行。别回来了，T。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~The problem ain't gone away, Tony. He's gonna come right back at us. We're still fucked, bro. I'll talk to you soon.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~麻烦还没完，Tony。他会回来找我们的，情况还是那样，兄弟。晚点再聊。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Hey man, I did what I could, bro.
~z~You fucking made it... man, that was some serious gangster shit.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你他妈做到了...天，那可是黑帮大战啊。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You're a fucking joke, man. All the money in the world and you can't get shit done.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你真他妈搞笑，哥们。给你全世界的钱都办不成事。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Fuck the people. Fuck them all! Whip out your dick and piss all over them.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~什么人不人的，都滚犊子！掏出你的大屌，滋他们一脸。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~This is not so hospitable, Mr. hospitality man.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~这样子招待客人不够意思啊，服务员先生。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Tony, man, I ain't gonna take you into a fiesta full of angry Russian gangsters
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Tony啊，我是不会带你进疯毛子窝的。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~What do you mean? If we go down, we go down together.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~这啥意思？要死我们就一起死啊。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Fuck Ray Bulgarin, fuck the mob, fuck the loan sharks, fuck the angry triads, the moaning celebrities, fuck everybody, Lou.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~什么高利贷，什么三合会，什么名流，全都滚犊子，Lou。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~If I survive this shit, I'll find you. If I don't show, then I'm gone.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~万一活下来了，我来找你。没来的话，就是死了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Yeah, well, I'm strong enough to kill your ass.
~z~Damn. They gotta be hiding out round the other side.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~妈的，他们肯定躲到另一边去了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I ain't that fucking cheery, bro. Later.
~z~I ain't letting you make no profit.
~z~It's not like I haven't been in my share of fire fights, Lou. By now, I'm a seasoned veteran by anyone's fucking standards!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我又不是没见过枪战，Lou。现在，怎么说我也算是身经百战的老兵了！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Fuck you all! I don't care what people say.
~z~You're going to go a long way in hospitality, my friend.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~待客这块你得好好学学了，朋友。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Luis, I love you, man. I love you.
~z~Stay away, Yusuf. You don't need to get involved with this. I'll call you if I make it out.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~不用了，Yusuf。别掺和进来。完事了我打电话给你。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I will get you done, you bitch.
~z~Protect the shipment with your pathetic little lives.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~牺牲你们的小命也要保住货！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~That's great! He's out of here. We can rest easy.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~那太好了！他走了，我们就安宁了。
~z~那好，你也得跟来。什么Ray Bulgarin，什么黑帮，

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You! Over there! You fuck with Luis Lopez you get one angry fucking Arab on your ass!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你！敢跟Luis Lopez对着干，就等着被阿拉伯暴脾气干烂吧！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You the man, Lopez. Kick their asses.
~z~- Wassup, my niggas? ~n~ '- Oh, did he just say that?
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~－还好吗，黑鬼们？~n~－噢，我没听错吧？

E2T11AU.original: ~z~No, you fuck off, Tony. I didn't kill you. I wanted to. Why? Because you've become a useless junkie fuck, that's why.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你才该滚出去，Tony。我没下手，只是有想过。为什么？因为你现在就是个吸毒废物，死了算了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Tony, bro, I love you, but I should handle this alone. I don't want you getting yourself killed.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Tony，好兄弟，我爱你，但这事得我自己处理。我可不想害死你。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I know that, bro, but there's no point in you coming in there. You can go off and die alone on some beach somewhere.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我知道，兄弟。但是你来没有意义啊。你走吧，找个海滩孤独终老吧。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You dumb bastard trying to screw with Luis Lopez! Bring it on, bitches!
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~哪个傻逼还敢跟Luis Lopez对着干！放马过来吧，臭逼！

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Tell Ray there an angry Dominican here to see him.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~告诉Ray，有个多米尼加疯子在找他。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I used to play round here when I was a kid,
~z~This is where the deal is meant to be.
~z~We did more than survive, amigo, we prospered.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~岂止是活下来了，朋友，我们发达了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~The Russian mob want me dead, my best friend just contemplated murdering me, the mob are on my case,
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~老毛子要我命，最好的朋友拿枪指着我，黑帮找我的麻烦，

E2T11AU.original: ~z~I got to get down the Dukes Expressway without any number of Russian assassins taking me down, or we're done.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~我得活着通过Dukes高速，不能被毛子杀手干掉，否则就完了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~You did it. You saved my life, you saved the business. You fucking did it.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~你做到了。救了我的命，挽救了生意。你他妈做到了。

E2T11AU.original: ~z~Mr. Ray has left, faggot. He already at airport.
E2T11AU.translated: ~z~Ray先生走了，基佬。他早就到机场了。
